      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's... exactly it. It's like being stuck in a room that's slowly filling with water and everyone around you is just pretending it's fine. It feels so irrational to keep pushing forward, you know? To keep working, making plans, caring about things... when it's all just going to be gone anyway. It feels more \"honest\" to just admit there's no point.",
